               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> <gramGrp> <pos expand="Substantivum">subst.</pos> <gen value="not found">m.</gen> </gramGrp> et. <gramGrp> <gen value="femininus">fem.</gen> </gramGrp> <sense n="1" xml:id="D1"> <sense n="a" xml:id="D1a"> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> donum sponsalicium </quote></cit>, quod sponsus futurae uxori in peculium dat;
</sense> <sense n="b" xml:id="D1b"> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> dos. </quote></cit> 
</sense> <sense n="c" xml:id="D1c"> De eo in F.N. 24 praecipitur: <foreign xml:lang="gez">እመ፡ ፈቀደ፡ ደኃሪ፡ አው፡ ዘተፍኅረት፡ ምንኵስና፡ እምድኅረ፡ ወሀበ፡ ሕፄ፡ ይደልዎ፡ ለደኃሪ፡ ዘወሀባ፡ ቅድመ፡ ከመ፡ ይንሣእ፡ ወለፍኅርቱኒ፡ ከመ፡ ታግብእ፡ ዘነሥአቶ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ካዕበት፡</foreign> (<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> nec duplicatione accepti mulctetur </quote></cit>); deinde 24,3, ubi voces <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዐረቦን፡ ዘፍኅረት፡</foreign> et <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሕፄ፡</foreign> promiscue usurpantur, haec statuuntur: <foreign xml:lang="gez">እምከመ፡ አበየ፡ ነሣኢሁ፡</foreign> (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ለዐራቦን፡</foreign>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">እምድኅረ፡ ተመጠወ፡ ኪያሁ፡ ወገደፋ፡ ለተሰናእዎ፡</foreign> (<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> consensum mutuum dissolvit </quote></cit>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ይሚጥ፡ ዘአኀዘ፡ ገቢሮ፡ ካዕበተ፡</foreign> (<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> reddat, quod accepit, duplicatum </quote></cit>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወእመ፡ ሞተት፡ ይእቲ፡ ብእሲት፡ ለያግብእ፡</foreign> (<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> repetat </quote></cit>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ደኃሪሃ፡ እምሰብአ፡ ዚአሃ፡ ዘወሀበ፡ በእንቲአሃ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ መብልዕ፡ ወመስቴ፡ ዘወሀበ። ወለእመ፡ ሞተ፡ ውእቱ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘሎቱ፡ ሕፄ፡</foreign> (<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> a quo donum datum est </quote></cit>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወአልቦቱ፡ ወራሲ፡ ይኅድጉ፡ ላቲ፡ ዘነሥአት፡ እምኀቤሁ፡ ወእመሰ፡ ቦቱ፡ ወራስያን፡ ያግብኡ፡ ሎሙ፡ መንፈቀ፡ ንዋዩ፡ ወመንፈቁ፡ ይትርፍ፡ ላቲ።</foreign> Ibidem <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሕፄ፡</foreign> distinguitur ab <foreign xml:lang="gez">አምኃ፡</foreign> i.e. muneribus variis, quae salutandi causa sponsus sponsae <gramGrp> <case value="dativus">dat.</case> </gramGrp> – In Bibliis respondet <foreign xml:lang="grc">φέρνη</foreign> <foreign xml:lang="he">מֹהַר</foreign>: <ref cRef="Gen." loc="34,12">Gen. 34,12</ref>; <ref cRef="Ex." loc="22,16">Ex. 22,16</ref> donum quod parentibus mulieris datur.
</sense> <sense n="d" xml:id="D1d"> <ref cRef="Jos." loc="16,10">Jos. 16,10</ref> dos quae a patre filiae datur; item <foreign xml:lang="gez">ይደሉ፡ አውስቦ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ትልወት፡ ወኢሕፄ፡</foreign> F.N. 24,3; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘጸሐፈ፡ ትእዛዘ፡</foreign> (i.e. <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> testator </quote></cit>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">የሀብ፡ ለአዌልዲሁ፡ ለለ፩ መክፈክተ፡ ሕፄሆን፡</foreign> F.N. 41,4.
</sense> 
</sense> <sense n="2" xml:id="D2"> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> donatio sponsalicia </quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> emtio sponsae </quote></cit>: F.N. 24,2; F.N. 24,3 ut: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዕድሜ፡ ሐዘን፡</foreign> (<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> tempus luctus definitum </quote></cit>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ይከልእ፡ እምአውስቦ፡</foreign> (<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> nuptias </quote></cit>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወኢይከልእ፡ እምሕፄ፡ ወእምፍኅረት።</foreign> 
</sense> </sense>
               
            <sense xml:id="Tmain" xml:lang="en" source="#traces"> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><quote>ḥǝḍe</quote></cit>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሕጼ፡</foreign> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><quote>ḥǝṣe</quote></cit> <sense n="G"> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሕጼ፡</foreign> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><quote>ḥǝṣe</quote></cit> «<cit type="translation" xml:lang="fr"><quote>donation de l’époux à l’épouse ou à ses parents, à l’ocassion des fiançailles</quote></cit>» ― <foreign xml:lang="am">እጅ፡ መንሻ፡</foreign> <foreign xml:lang="am">ማጫ፡</foreign> Ms. <ref type="BM" target="BNFabb217">BNFabb217</ref>, fol. 31r. <lb/>
 <bibl><ptr target="bm:Grebaut1952SuppLexicon"/><citedRange unit="page"> 68</citedRange></bibl> 
